Function Reference/get header textcolor « WordPress Codex
-----------

Retrieve text color for custom header.

Usage
-----

` <?php get_header_textcolor() ?> `

Parameters
----------

None.

Return Values
-------------

 (string) 
:   

Examples
--------

Notes
-----

-   Uses: `HEADER_TEXTCOLOR`

Change Log
----------

Since: 2.1.0

Source File
-----------

`get_header_textcolor()` is located in `wp-includes/theme.php`.

